'''[[Svenska Cupen]] 1941''' was the first season of the main [[Sweden|Swedish]] [[Association football|football]] Cup. The competition was concluded on 26 October 1941 with the [[1941 Svenska Cupen Final|Final]], held at [[Råsunda Stadium]], [[Solna Municipality|Solna]] in [[Stockholms län]]. [[Helsingborgs IF]] won the final 3-1 against [[IK Sleipner]] before an attendance of 10,763 spectators.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://svenskfotboll.se/svensk-fotboll/historia/historik-herrar/svenska-cupen/ |title=Svensk Fotboll - Historia - Svenska Cupens finaler 1941 - Svenskfotboll.se |format= |work= |accessdate=2011-10-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110814041638/http://svenskfotboll.se/svensk-fotboll/historia/historik-herrar/svenska-cupen/ |archivedate=14 August 2011 |df=dmy }}</ref>
